Package: SWDSFODR
Type: Package
Title: SWDSFODR - First Order Decay Methane Emissions from Solid Waste Disposal Sites
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
      given = "Luciano",
      family = "Caratori",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "luciano@caratori.com.ar",
    )
Description: 
  Implements the CDM "Tool 04: Emissions from solid waste disposal sites" (Version 08.1)
  using a First Order Decay (FOD) model. Includes both annual and monthly calculations,
  as well as simplified approaches for MSW. Also provides a Shiny UI to assist in 
  parameter input, scenario configuration, and results visualization.
